Package org.cloudbus.cloudsim

Class DataCloudTags

java.lang.Object
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.DataCloudTags
public final class DataCloudTags extends Object
This class contains additional tags for the DataCloud functionalities, such as file information retrieval, file transfers, and storage info.
Since:
CloudSim Toolkit 1.0
Author:
Uros Cibej, Anthony Sulistio
